{"tid":469900,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"真係唔好叫朋友一齊返工","createTime":"2017-11-15T19:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T13:34:42.000Z","uid":146917,"like":1512,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"56e21b4144d11360a4d3d478859b06cf233f6a56","tid":469900,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:09:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我返緊份part time都有一年幾，對d 同事叫有傾有講。<br />\n但我其實唔太中意對住同事講自己d 事，如果d 同事問起我都只會淡淡地輕描帶過，<br />\n咁我朋友得閒就想搵返工，咁我見佢都幾慘就介紹佢一齊做。<br />\n第一日，出事啦，d 同事問起我fd係點識我，我屌佢老味係咁講9我 d野，<br />\n我對同事同fd 係兩種手法，我fd係咁拆穿我，我心諗，真係多9謝你，一日搞撚鍋我做左一年ga工，依架令我唔想返，最後我想講，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老尾</span></span>。"},{"pid":"df57b52de354db9d3f4f6a5c9e72bd20e290911f","tid":469900,"uid":146917,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人同意？"},{"pid":"0eca490f81647e652da4ecefa2989ca8b7cb89e0","tid":469900,"uid":63132,"like":290,"dislike":3,"score":287,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"唔同case,<br />\n不過同fd一齊返工真係好易嗌交,<br />\n尤其是一個senior啲嘅帶人入去做,<br />\n新嗰個做得唔好又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c090ca38397ae611d38819ea4b21e00f536c9f","tid":469900,"uid":10208,"like":329,"dislike":3,"score":326,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:26:54.000Z","msg":"佢做錯野 之後其他同事就會話<br />\n「喂，話下你個fd唔好再xxxxx」<br />\n<br />\n我普通講佢又當我講笑，唔認真改<br />\n下次佢有咩錯，其他同事就會怪你<br />\n<br />\n認真講既話佢可能又會同朋友圈既人講<br />\n話我持住早佢入職就係到扮老屎忽，鬧人<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0381fb52eb8a95fcc8b832783e05389099