刻無人知你過去<br />\n只知你係一位新同事<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"b7c745a42e03ee41f5538ed9bc81b57058130bf2","tid":469900,"uid":146917,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢做錯野 之後其他同事就會話<br />\n「喂，話下你個fd唔好再xxxxx」<br />\n<br />\n我普通講佢又當我講笑，唔認真改<br />\n下次佢有咩錯，其他同事就會怪你<br />\n<br />\n認真講既話佢可能又會同朋友圈既人講<br />\n話我持住早佢入職就係到扮老屎忽，鬧人<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要你fd 做錯事d 同事屌你先on9<br />\n心諗關我撚事"},{"pid":"2bcf35057d568bb86cc7155b5e0474c0a6b4cb24","tid":469900,"uid":85993,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:35:29.000Z","msg":"完全同意<br />\n我都有試過<br />\n一直自己都唔會同同事講感情事<br />\n一介紹左個朋友黎返<br />\n就直頭係我面前講我啲野<br />\n仲要我開左口話唔好講<br />\n屌 勁撚八掛同唔尊重人"},{"pid":"d8225e0be5990ae1df1307bc4f38749c53bae7d8","tid":469900,"uid":89270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:35:41.000Z","msg":"之前試過一齊返一日都想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9741a255f9512d8659213ffaa51de318c3a49278","tid":469900,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全同意<br />\n我都有試過<br />\n一直自己都唔會同同事講感情事<br />\n一介紹左個朋友黎返<br />\n就直頭係我面前講我啲野<br />\n仲要我開左口話唔好講<br />\n屌 勁撚八掛同唔尊重人</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚on9 有時候係到真係自己一個返仲開心"},{"pid":"3d9948896486170890041de5d26f1756c9373322","tid":469900,"uid":6060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:39:02.000Z","msg":"通常翻office 就會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22436d9894e2e91b5fa37e659a16c4c82db77ae","tid":469900,"uid